title: Jack McDevitt - The Devil's Eye (Alex Benedict #4)
description:
Jack McDevitt - The Devil's Eye (Alex Benedict #4)

Read by Jennifer Van Dyck
Format: MP3
Unabridged

Interstellar antiquities dealer Alex Benedict receives a cryptic message asking for help from celebrated writer Vicki Greene - who has been mind-wiped. She has no memory of her past life, or of her plea for assistance. But she has transferred an enormous sum of money to Alex, also without explanation. The answers to this mystery lie on the most remote of human worlds, where Alex will uncover a secret connected to a decades-old political upheaval - a secret that somebody desperately wants hidden, though the price of that silence is unimaginable.Bonus Audio: Includes an exclusive introduction by author Jack McDevitt
